    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "im not really in a crisis i just feel physically unwell and sick. i know the diazepam is for my anxiety but since this feels like a physical panic reaction, i thought it might stop the chest tightness. if i just take a half dose like i usually do for the panic attacks, will that be safe enough to just get me through the night? i'm mostly just scared of the chest feeling, but i really dont want to deal with doctors right now if i can just sleep it off.",
